properties.name: 14 May 2009 Wallah 5000 people displaced
properties.description:
On behalf of Bor RCSO,

I would like to invite all concerned parties to a meeting to discuss the alleged 5000 displaced people in Wallah.

Date/Time: Today at 14:30
Venue: UNHCR hall

Thank you and apologies for the short notice

Antoine


Note Marker is not  on Wallah as I have not been able to  locate exact village yet

properties.name: 14 May 2009 atleast 1000 displaced
properties.description:
NAIROBI, 14 May 2009 (IRIN) - Thousands of civilians have fled inter-ethnic fighting in Southern Sudan's Upper Nile State, with at least 1,000 on the outskirts of Nasir town, the medical charity Médecins Sans Frontières (MSF) said.
